review: Abesloutely Stunning, well job, a thing that I would like to see that's most likely impossible is mod support, that would be awesome.

Okay, DayZ is one of those games where it will give you a cookie, you will be happy. But then suddenly DayZ takes that cookie away from you and punches you in the face, then it eats the cookie. Then that cycle repeats..... 46/10 - would keep getting punched in the face for cookies again.
